{"tid":2272901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【蘋果新聞？】美國大選︱袁彌昌料拜登上場續防中國稱霸","createTime":"2020-11-05T10:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T11:47:18.000Z","uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9ee511f7ba45d537a57310c832e2a9ba08f58cc1","tid":2272901,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"美國大選︱袁彌昌料拜登上場續防中國稱霸 梁啟智：理解部份港人希望特朗普勝選<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/LOUWWQ4QCJHCZOI5LI2A24OXKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FLOUWWQ4QCJHCZOI5LI2A24OXKE%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4JKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=fbca3dcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FLOUWWQ4QCJHCZOI5LI2A24OXKE%2F&h=9609c654\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/LOUWWQ4QCJHCZOI5LI2A24OXKE/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rRhTCVj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrRhTCVj.png&h=9923c568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">有學者指</span></strong>，即使由民主黨拜登入主白宮，對華政策不會變得軟弱。<br />\n<br />\n美國大選因為現任總統特朗普提出訴訟，未必在短時間內有終極點票結果，但拜登暫時勝算較大。有學者指，即使由民主黨拜登入主白宮，對華政策不會變得軟弱；另亦有學者稱，理解香港人為何希望特朗普勝選，相信去年的反修例運動，令大家有情感上的投射。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BA2MdtS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBA2MdtS.png&h=a3cbf931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">國際關係學者袁彌昌</span></strong>指以目前資訊而言，特朗普或「大勢已去」，指今次大選可見美國人表現十分克制及有紀律，扭轉不少人對美國的印象。他不相信有指拜登上場對華會太軟弱，指美國對華政策由「友好」轉為「不友善」，始於奧巴馬時代，而拜登當時為副總統，也是政策制訂者之一，預料他會延續防止中國成為東亞地區霸權的方向，但相信在貿易問題上，拜登可以商量的空間較大。<br />\n<br />\n梁啟智部份請入連結觀看<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我聞到人民幣既味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c04ac1b3033464724ad50d31de367d313d45a1d","tid":2272901,"uid":224479,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:04:09.000Z","msg":"袁彌昌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5c23cf7b652d5d0087f0223aaeb2a383ec3c34","tid":2272901,"uid":326665,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:05:09.000Z","msg":"防咋，唔係滅呀"},{"pid":"67d60a71c21b4ca1034eb8d1ab4dc99d8be36cd1","tid":2272901,"uid":57843,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:06:09.000Z","msg":"I'm an egghead"},{"pid":"a014160a6bc8ef0e0433634f6be7935acd2958b9","tid":2272901,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3c04ac1b3033464724ad50d31de367d313d45a1d","tid":2272901,"uid":224479,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:04:09.000Z","msg":"袁彌昌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"第一次見彌唱以專家身份上蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a1a9067e9afc50dafeb7aa6e8f34a997842620","tid":2272901,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3c04ac1b3033464724ad50d31de367d313d45a1d","tid":2272901,"uid":224479,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:04:09.000Z","msg":"袁彌昌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:31:53.000Z","msg":"連孽瘤都嫌佢廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82416324bfd3e1b43ce11f5781dbca5d43ae9d2","tid":2272901,"uid":34065,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"袁彌昌 就算撚數 叫佢返屋企同佢老婆奶閪算啦"},{"pid":"45037a0d450218e3b533b17c84aaf1c42e11792c","tid":2272901,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:41:27.000Z","msg":"邊撚度學者呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d5d3a928ffe1c1a9c7cab2f8cf23fd1d9f3e40","tid":2272901,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:47:18.000Z","msg":"我認為「學者」應該好似醫生咁, 要考牌<br />\n<br />\n家陣睇新聞, 阿豬阿狗都話自己係學者"}]}